.TH wxGraphicsPen 3 "wx 2.5.4" "Ericsson AB" "Erlang Module Definition"
.SH NAME
wxGraphicsPen \- A \fIwxGraphicsPen\fR is a native representation of a pen.

.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
The contents are specific and private to the respective renderer. Instances are ref counted and can therefore be assigned as usual. The only way to get a valid instance is via \fIwxGraphicsContext:createPen/2\fR or \fIwxGraphicsRenderer::CreatePen()\fR (not implemented in wx).

.PP
